This Kid Helping His Little Sister Play Basketball Is The Joy We All Need|http://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk|http://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/entry/kid-helps-his-little-sister-play-basketball-video_uk_5bc9b582e4b0d38b58771366?ncid=other_topnaventr_coabgdcpxri&utm_campaign=topnav||2018-10-19|Sophie Gallagher,Reporter At Huffpost Uk||A video of a little boy helping his younger sister learn how to shoot basketball hoops has gone viral after showing just how nice siblings can be to each other.

The 20-second clip shows the girl trying to get a basket but failing and dropping the ball on her face – which makes her cry.

Instead of getting angry or just taking the ball from her and showing her how it is done, the brother comforts his sister and says: “It’s okay, you’re strong.”
